{"tid":930051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"配件商哭哭！iPhone XR官方透明保護殼真的上市了","createTime":"2018-12-06T04:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T04:47:47.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed5298b9745f5d5e15aba158a2431ecace963fae","tid":930051,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:34:52.000Z","msg":"蘋果在9月12日發表三款全新iPhone，包括兩支雙鏡頭6.5吋的iPhoneXS Max和5.8吋的iPhone XS，以及價格相對親民（2萬6900元起）的單鏡頭手機iPhone XR，並且有6色設計，也能吸引更多年輕族群。<br />\n <br />\n而先前報導，相較以往蘋果除了推出矽膠與皮革外殼，也可能因應有白、黑、藍、黃、珊瑚和紅（product Red）6色設計的iPhone XR，釋出旗下首款塑膠透明保護殼，讓機背顏色不會被保護殼掩蓋。<br />\n <br />\n現在iPhone XR透明保護殼真的釋出了，已可開放購買要價1190元。官方網頁說明為「這款保護殼纖薄、輕巧，且輕鬆好握，不但可呈現iPhone XR 的外觀，還能提供額外的保護。保護殼的內外層表面，都加上抗刮塗層。需要以無線方式充電嗎？無須拆下保護殼，直接將iPhone 放在 Qi 認證充電器上即可。」"},{"pid":"47be55876ecd727a07fde78a0a1bf610f28c0498","tid":930051,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:37:10.000Z","msg":"Hello無圖"},{"pid":"ed32e2e376671ac572b78368fdf1f5f9426a1495","tid":930051,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:39:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181206/1479029/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181206%2F1479029%2F&d=25lWIakmnjXfrruxfuQJpf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=67e5f39a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181206%2F1479029%2F&h=108f49c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181206/1479029/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181206/640_d613b690ef9ec9ee058e9b48ef54783e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181206%2F640_d613b690ef9ec9ee058e9b48ef54783e.jpg&h=194dffdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n透明殻嚟，搵鬼買咩"},{"pid":"c7b4a6a0411a1c866faf2d3c70a13354338b960a","tid":930051,"uid":32486,"lik